# Políticas IAM para OCI Kubernetes Storage Classes

## Compartimento
```
alemanasantiago:dr:app:poc_oke
```

## 1. Grupo Dinámico
```
Nombre: k8s-dynamic-group
Descripción: Dynamic group for Kubernetes cluster nodes

Reglas de coincidencia:
ALL {instance.compartment.id = 'alemanasantiago:dr:app:poc_oke'}
ANY {instance.displayname = /.*k8s.*/, instance.displayname = /.*kubernetes.*/, instance.displayname = /.*worker.*/, instance.displayname = /.*node.*/}
```

## 2. Políticas de Block Storage

### k8s-block-storage-management-policy
```
Descripción: Policy for Kubernetes Block Storage CSI driver operations

Declaraciones:
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage volume-family in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage volume-attachments in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage instances in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to read compartments in tenancy
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to read availability-domains in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to use subnets in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to use vnics in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to use network-security-groups in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
```

### k8s-block-storage-backup-policy
```
Descripción: Policy for Kubernetes Block Storage backup operations

Declaraciones:
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage volume-backups in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage volume-backup-policies in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
```

## 3. Políticas de File Storage Service

### k8s-file-storage-management-policy
```
Descripción: Policy for Kubernetes File Storage Service (FSS) CSI driver operations

Declaraciones:
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage file-family in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage mount-targets in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage export-sets in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage file-systems in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to read compartments in tenancy
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to read availability-domains in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to use subnets in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to use vnics in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to use network-security-groups in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
```

### k8s-file-storage-snapshot-policy
```
Descripción: Policy for Kubernetes File Storage Service snapshot operations

Declaraciones:
Allow dynamic-group k8s-nodes to manage file-system-snapshots in compartment dr:app:poc_oke
```

## Resumen de Permisos

### Permisos de Block Storage:
- Gestión completa de volúmenes y adjuntos de volúmenes
- Gestión de instancias
- Operaciones de respaldo de volúmenes
- Lectura de compartimentos y dominios de disponibilidad
- Uso de recursos de red (subnets, VNICs, NSGs)

### Permisos de File Storage:
- Gestión completa de sistemas de archivos
- Gestión de puntos de montaje y conjuntos de exportación
- Operaciones de snapshots de sistemas de archivos
- Lectura de compartimentos y dominios de disponibilidad
- Uso de recursos de red (subnets, VNICs, NSGs)

### Grupo Dinámico:
- Incluye todas las instancias del compartimento alemanasantiago:dr:app:poc_oke
- Filtra por nombres que contengan: k8s, kubernetes, worker, node




